📊 Advanced Bank Loan Data Analysis Dashboard
Empowering Data-Driven Decision-Making in Lending Operations

This repository presents a comprehensive Power BI analytical solution designed to transform raw loan data into dynamic, actionable insights. Built to overcome the limitations of traditional reporting, this interactive dashboard suite enables financial institutions to monitor performance, assess risk, and understand borrower behavior with precision.

🎯 Key Features
Executive Summary: Real-time KPIs including total loan applications, funded & received amounts, average interest rate, and debt-to-income (DTI) ratio.
Loan Performance by Status: Detailed breakdown of loans by status — Fully Paid, Charged Off, and Current — with metrics on funding, repayments, and interest trends.
Borrower Insights: Visual analysis of applications by:
Employment length
Loan purpose (e.g., debt consolidation, credit card, small business)
Home ownership status
Loan term (36 vs 60 months)
Geographic distribution by state
Time-Series Trends: Monthly tracking of loan applications and funding to identify seasonal patterns and growth opportunities.
Interactive Filters: Fully dynamic dashboards with slicers for Grade, Term, Purpose, and Good vs Bad Loan segmentation.
📈 Business Value
Identify high-risk loan segments and improve underwriting strategies.
Track cash flow health through funded vs. received amounts.
Monitor lending trends and performance month-over-month (MoM).
Support strategic decisions with visual, intuitive, and drill-through analytics.
🛠️ Tools Used
Power BI Desktop
DAX for calculated measures and KPIs
Data Modeling for efficient relationships and performance
Custom Visuals & Conditional Formatting for enhanced readability
